<lb n="0795c12" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="001"/><cb:jhead>佛說五王經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0795c13" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0795c14"/><byline cb:type="Translator">失譯<note n="0795011" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔人名〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0795011" type="mod" resp="CBETA">人名【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0795011"><lem wit="【大】">人名</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>今附東晉錄</byline>
<lb n="0795c15" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0795c1501"><note n="0795012" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">昔＋（者）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0795012">昔【大】，昔者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795012"><lem wit="【大】">昔</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">昔者</rdg></app>有五王，國界相近，共相往來，不相攻伐，
<lb n="0795c16" ed="T"/>唯作善友。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0795c1605" rend="inline">其最大者，字普安王，習菩薩行；
<lb ed="T" n="0795c17"/>餘四小王，常習邪行。大王<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0795013">（憐愍…之）六字＝愍之【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0795013">（憐愍…之）六字【大】，愍之【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="6" n="0795013"><lem wit="【大】">憐愍，意欲度之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">愍之</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0795c18" ed="T"/>呼來上殿，共相娛樂，乃至七日，終日竟夜，
<lb ed="T" n="0795c19"/>作倡伎樂。七日已滿，四<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0795014">王＝小王【三】【宮】</note><note n="0795014" type="mod" resp="CBETA">王【大】，小王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795014"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">小王</rdg></app>共白<note n="0795c1901" resp="CBETA" type="add">大【CB】【麗-CB】，天【大】</note><app n="0795c1901"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">大<note type="cf1">K20n0863_p1227a08</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">天</rdg></app>王言：「國
<lb ed="T" n="0795c20"/>事甚多，請還政治。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0795c2008">大王語諸左右：「嚴駕車
<lb ed="T" n="0795c21"/>乘，群臣吏民都共送之。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0795c2110" rend="inline">至其半道，大王憐
<lb n="0795c22" ed="T"/>愍，意欲度之，語<note n="0795015" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">（四王…言）十四字＝諸小王曰各說所樂悅樂之情一王答言【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0795015a">（四王…事）十一字【大】，諸小王曰各說所樂悅樂之情一王答言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795015a" cb:word-count="14"><lem wit="【大】">四王言：「各說卿等所樂之
<lb ed="T" n="0795c23"/>事。」</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">諸小王曰各說所樂悅樂之情</rdg></app></p><p xml:id="pT14p0795c2302" rend="inline"><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0795015b">一王言【大】，一王答言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="14" n="0795015b"><lem wit="【大】">一王言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">一王答言</rdg></app>：「我願欲得陽春三月，樹木榮華，遊
<lb ed="T" n="0795c24"/>戲原野，是我<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0795016">所樂＝之樂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0795016" type="mod" resp="CBETA">所樂【大】，之樂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795016"><lem wit="【大】">所樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">之樂</rdg></app>。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0795c2408" rend="inline">一王復言：「<note n="0795017" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">我願欲得＝我所樂異願我【三】【宮】</note><note n="0795017" type="mod" resp="CBETA">我願欲得【大】，我所樂異願我【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795017"><lem wit="【大】">我願欲得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">我所樂異願我</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0795c25"/>常作國王，鞍馬服飾，樓閣殿堂，官屬人民
<lb n="0795c26" ed="T"/>圍遶左右，晃晃昱<anchor xml:id="fxT14p0795c02"/>昱，<note n="0795018" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">椎＝搥【三】【宮】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0795018"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->椎【大】＊，搥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0795018"><lem wit="【大】">椎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">搥</rdg></app>鍾鳴鼓，出入行
<lb ed="T" n="0795c27"/>來，路人傾目，是我之樂。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0795c2710">一王復言：「我所樂
<lb ed="T" n="0795c28"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0795019">復異願＝異願復【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0795019">復異願【大】，異願復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0795019"><lem wit="【大】">復異。願</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">異願復</rdg></app>得好婦、好兒，端正無雙，共相娛樂，
<lb ed="T" n="0795c29"/>極情<note n="0795020" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">快意＝快樂【宮】</note><note n="0795020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">快意【大】，快樂【宮】</note><app n="0795020"><lem wit="【大】">快意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">快樂</rdg></app>，是我之樂。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0795c2909" rend="inline">一王復言：「我所樂復
<pb xml:id="T14.0523.0796a" n="0796a" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0796a01"/>異。願我父母常在，多有兄弟、妻子，羅列好
<lb ed="T" n="0796a02"/>衣美食，以恣其口，素<anchor xml:id="fxT14p0796a01"/>琴<note n="0796001" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">清衣＝青衣【三】＊【宮】</note><note n="0796001" type="mod" resp="CBETA">清衣【大】＊，青衣【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊【宮】</note><app n="0796001"><lem wit="【大】">清衣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">青衣</rdg></app>，共相娛樂，
<lb n="0796a03" ed="T"/><note n="0796002" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">〔是我之樂〕－【宮】</note><note n="0796002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是我之樂【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0796002"><lem wit="【大】">是我之樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0796a0305" rend="inline">各自說其所樂竟，四王俱迴頭
<lb n="0796a04" ed="T"/>白其大王：「<note n="0796003" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔王〕－【宮】</note><note n="0796003" type="mod" resp="CBETA">王【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0796003"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>所樂何事？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796a0410">大王答言：「我先說
<lb n="0796a05" ed="T"/>卿等<note n="0796004" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">所樂＝不樂【宮】</note><note n="0796004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所樂【大】，不樂【宮】</note><app n="0796004"><lem wit="【大】">所樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">不樂</rdg></app>，然後說我之樂。卿一人言『陽春
<lb ed="T" n="0796a06"/>三月，樹木榮華，遊戲原野』，秋則<note n="0796005" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">凋＝彫【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796005">凋【大】，彫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796005"><lem wit="【大】">凋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">彫</rdg></app>落，非
<lb n="0796a07" ed="T"/>是久樂。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796a0704">「卿一人<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796006">（復）＋言【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0796006" type="mod" resp="CBETA">言【大】＊，復言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0796006"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復言</rdg></app>『願我常作國王，鞍馬服
<lb n="0796a08" ed="T"/>飾，樓閣殿堂，官屬人民圍遶左右，晃晃昱
<lb ed="T" n="0796a09"/>昱，椎<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0796007">鍾＝種【元】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0796007">鍾【大】，種【元】</note><app n="0796007"><lem wit="【大】">鍾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">種</rdg></app>鳴鼓，出入行來，路人傾目』，往古
<lb n="0796a10" ed="T"/>諸王，隱隱<note n="0796008" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">闐闐＝軫軫【宋】【元】，賑賑【明】【宮】</note><note n="0796008" type="mod" resp="CBETA">闐闐【大】，軫軫【宋】【元】，賑賑【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796008"><lem wit="【大】">闐闐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">軫軫</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">賑賑</rdg></app>，快樂無極，福德轉盡，諸國
<lb n="0796a11" ed="T"/>相伐，忽然崩亡，非是久樂。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0796a1111" rend="inline">「卿一人<app corresp="#0796006" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復言</rdg></app>『願
<lb n="0796a12" ed="T"/>得好婦、好兒，端正無雙，共相娛樂，極情快意』，
<lb n="0796a13" ed="T"/>一朝疾病，憂苦無量，<note n="0796009" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">非是＝此非【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796009">非是【大】，此非【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796009"><lem wit="【大】">非是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">此非</rdg></app>久樂。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796a1313">「卿一人<app type="star" corresp="#0796006"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">復言</rdg></app>
<lb n="0796a14" ed="T"/>『願我父母常在，多有兄弟、妻子，羅列好衣美
<lb ed="T" n="0796a15"/>食，以恣其口，素琴<app corresp="#0796001" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">清衣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">青衣</rdg></app>，共相娛樂』，一朝
<lb n="0796a16" ed="T"/>有事，為官<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0796010">所執＝所攝【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0796010">所執【大】，所攝【宮】</note><app n="0796010"><lem wit="【大】">所執</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">所攝</rdg></app>，繫閉在獄，無有救護，此非
<lb n="0796a17" ed="T"/>久樂。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0796a1703" rend="inline">四人俱問：「王樂<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796011">何事＝云何【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796011" type="mod" resp="CBETA">何事【大】，云何【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796011"><lem wit="【大】">何事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">云何</rdg></app>？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0796a1711" rend="inline">王言：「我樂不生
<lb ed="T" n="0796a18"/>不死，不苦不<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796012">惱＝樂【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796012">惱【大】，樂【元】【明】</note><app n="0796012"><lem wit="【大】">惱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">樂</rdg></app>，不饑不渴，不寒不熱，存亡
<lb ed="T" n="0796a19"/>自在，此是我樂。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0796a1907" rend="inline">四王俱言：「此樂何處？當有
<lb n="0796a20" ed="T"/>明師？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0796a2003" rend="inline">大王答言：「吾師<note n="0796013" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">號＋（曰）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796013">號【大】，號曰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796013"><lem wit="【大】">號</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">號曰</rdg></app>為佛，近在<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0796014">祇桓＝祇洹【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796014" type="mod" resp="CBETA">祇桓【大】，祇洹【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796014"><lem wit="【大】">祇桓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">祇洹</rdg></app>精
<lb ed="T" n="0796a21"/>舍。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796a2102">諸王歡喜，各詣佛所，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796015">〔皆〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796015">皆【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796015"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>稽首作禮，退坐
<lb ed="T" n="0796a22"/>一面。大王胡跪，<note n="0796016" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">叉手＝合掌【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796016" type="mod" resp="CBETA">叉手【大】，合掌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796016"><lem wit="【大】">叉手</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">合掌</rdg></app>白佛言：「我等今得為
<lb n="0796a23" ed="T"/>人，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796017">鈍闇＝闇鈍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796017" type="mod" resp="CBETA">鈍闇【大】，闇鈍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796017"><lem wit="【大】">鈍闇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">闇鈍</rdg></app>無<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0796018">智＝知【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796018" type="mod" resp="CBETA">智【大】，知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796018"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">知</rdg></app>，但深著世樂，不知罪福。願
<lb n="0796a24" ed="T"/>佛為弟子等，說其苦諦。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0796a2410" rend="inline">佛言：「卿等善聽！當
<lb n="0796a25" ed="T"/>為汝說。人生在世，常有無量眾苦切身，今
<lb n="0796a26" ed="T"/>粗為汝等略說八苦。何謂八苦？生苦、老苦、病
<lb n="0796a27" ed="T"/>苦、死苦、恩愛別苦、所求不得苦、怨憎會苦、
<lb ed="T" n="0796a28"/>憂悲惱苦。是為八苦也。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796a2810">「何謂生苦？人死之
<lb n="0796a29" ed="T"/>時，不知精神趣向何道，<note n="0796019" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">未得＝未知【宮】</note><note n="0796019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未得【大】，未知【宮】</note><app n="0796019"><lem wit="【大】">未得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">未知</rdg></app>生處，並受中
<pb xml:id="T14.0523.0796b" ed="T" n="0796b"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0796b01"/>陰之形，至三七<note n="0796020" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">日＋（中）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796020" type="mod" resp="CBETA">日【大】，日中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796020"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">日中</rdg></app>父母和合，便來受胎。一
<lb ed="T" n="0796b02"/>七日如薄酪；二七日如稠酪；三七日如凝酥；
<lb n="0796b03" ed="T"/>四七日如肉臠，五<note n="0796021" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">皰＝胞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796021" type="mod" resp="CBETA">皰【大】，胞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796021"><lem wit="【大】">皰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">胞</rdg></app>成就，巧風入腹，吹其
<lb ed="T" n="0796b04"/>身體，六情開張。在母腹中，生藏之下，熟藏
<lb n="0796b05" ed="T"/>之上，母噉一杯熱食，灌其身體，如入鑊湯；
<lb ed="T" n="0796b06"/>母飲一杯冷水，亦如寒氷切體；母飽之時，迫
<lb n="0796b07" ed="T"/><note n="0796022" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">迮＝逼【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796022" type="mod" resp="CBETA">迮【大】，逼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796022"><lem wit="【大】">迮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">逼</rdg></app>身體，痛不可言；母饑之時，腹中了了，亦
<lb ed="T" n="0796b08"/>如倒懸，受苦無量。至其滿月，欲生<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796023">〔之時〕－【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796023">之時【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0796023"><lem wit="【大】">之時</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，頭
<lb ed="T" n="0796b09"/><note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0796024">（下）＋向【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796024" type="mod" resp="CBETA">向【大】，下向【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796024"><lem wit="【大】">向</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">下向</rdg></app>產門，<note n="0796025" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">〔劇〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796025">劇【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796025"><lem wit="【大】">劇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>如兩石<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0796026">挾＝夾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796026" type="mod" resp="CBETA">挾【大】，夾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796026"><lem wit="【大】">挾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">夾</rdg></app>山；欲生之時，母危
<lb ed="T" n="0796b10"/>父怖。生墮草上，身體細軟，草觸其身，如履
<lb ed="T" n="0796b11"/>刀劍，忽然失聲大<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0796027">呼＝喚【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796027">呼【大】，喚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796027"><lem wit="【大】">呼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">喚</rdg></app>。此是苦不？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796b1113">諸人咸言：
<lb n="0796b12" ed="T"/>「<note n="0796028" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">此＝實【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796028" type="mod" resp="CBETA">此【大】，實【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796028"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">實</rdg></app>是大苦。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796b1205">「何謂老苦？父母養育，至年長大，
<lb ed="T" n="0796b13"/>自用強健，擔輕負重，不自裁量，寒時極寒，
<lb n="0796b14" ed="T"/>熱時極熱，饑時極饑，飽時極飽，無有節度；漸
<lb n="0796b15" ed="T"/>至年老，頭白齒落，目視<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796029">𥆨𥆨＝茫茫【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796029">𥆨𥆨【大】，茫茫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0796029"><lem wit="【大】">𥆨𥆨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">茫茫</rdg></app>，耳聽不聰，盛
<lb n="0796b16" ed="T"/>去衰至，皮緩面皺，百節<note n="0796030" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">痠＝痛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796030" type="mod" resp="CBETA">痠【大】，痛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796030"><lem wit="【大】">痠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">痛</rdg></app>疼，行步苦極，坐
<lb n="0796b17" ed="T"/>起呻吟，憂悲心惱，識神轉滅，便旋即忘，命
<lb n="0796b18" ed="T"/>日促盡，言之流涕，坐起須人。此是苦不？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0796b1816" rend="inline">大
<lb n="0796b19" ed="T"/>王答曰：「實是大苦。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796b1908">「何謂病苦？人有四大，和
<lb ed="T" n="0796b20"/>合而成其身——何謂四大？地大、水大、火大、風大——
<lb n="0796b21" ed="T"/>一大不調，百一病生，四大不調，四百四病
<lb ed="T" n="0796b22"/>同時<note n="0796031" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">俱＝共【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796031" type="mod" resp="CBETA">俱【大】，共【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796031"><lem wit="【大】">俱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">共</rdg></app>作。地大不調，舉身<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796032">沈重＝皆痛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796032" type="mod" resp="CBETA">沈重【大】，皆痛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796032"><lem wit="【大】">沈重</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">皆痛</rdg></app>；水大不
<lb n="0796b23" ed="T"/>調，舉身<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0796033">膖＝肨【宋】【元】，胮【明】，皆胖【宮】</note><note n="0796033" type="mod" resp="CBETA">膖【大】，肨【宋】【元】，胮【明】，皆胖【宮】</note><app n="0796033"><lem wit="【大】">膖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">肨</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">胮</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">皆胖</rdg></app>腫；火大不調，舉身蒸熱；風大不
<lb n="0796b24" ed="T"/>調，舉身掘強，百節苦痛，猶被杖楚。四大進
<lb n="0796b25" ed="T"/>退，手足不任，氣力虛竭，坐起須人，口燥脣
<lb ed="T" n="0796b26"/>燋，筋斷鼻<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796034">坼＝拆【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796034">坼【大】，拆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796034"><lem wit="【大】">坼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">拆</rdg></app>，目不見色，耳不聞<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796035">聲＝音【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796035">聲【大】，音【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796035"><lem wit="【大】">聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">音</rdg></app>，不淨
<lb ed="T" n="0796b27"/>流出，身臥其上，心懷苦惱，言輒悲哀，六親
<lb n="0796b28" ed="T"/>在側，晝夜<note n="0796036" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">看視初不＝看侍初無【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796036">看視初不【大】，看侍初無【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796036"><lem wit="【大】">看視初不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">看侍初無</rdg></app>休息，甘饍美食，入口
<lb n="0796b29" ed="T"/>皆苦。此是苦不？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796b2907"><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796037">答言＝王答曰【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796037">答言【大】，王答曰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796037"><lem wit="【大】">答言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">王答曰</rdg></app>：「實是大苦。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796b2913">「何謂死苦？
<pb n="0796c" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0523.0796c"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0796c01"/>人死之時，四百四病，同時俱作，四大欲散，
<lb ed="T" n="0796c02"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796038">魂魄＝魂神【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796038">魂魄【大】，魂神【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796038"><lem wit="【大】">魂魄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">魂神</rdg></app>不安。欲死之時，刀風解形，無處不痛，
<lb n="0796c03" ed="T"/>白汗流出，兩手摸空。室家內外，在其左右，
<lb n="0796c04" ed="T"/>憂悲涕<note n="0796039" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">泣＝哭【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796039">泣【大】，哭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796039"><lem wit="【大】">泣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">哭</rdg></app>，痛徹骨髓，不能自勝。死者去之，
<lb n="0796c05" ed="T"/>風去氣絕，火滅身冷，風先火次。魂靈去矣，
<lb n="0796c06" ed="T"/>身體<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796040">侹＝<g ref="#CB13439"/>【宋】【宮】，挺【元】【明】</note><note n="0796040" type="mod" resp="CBETA">侹【大】，<g ref="#CB13439"/>【宋】【宮】，挺【元】【明】</note><app n="0796040"><lem wit="【大】">侹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】"><g ref="#CB13439"/></rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">挺</rdg></app>直，無所復知。旬日之間，肉壞血流，
<lb n="0796c07" ed="T"/>膖脹爛臭，甚不可<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796041">道＝近【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796041" type="mod" resp="CBETA">道【大】，近【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796041"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">近</rdg></app>，棄之曠野，眾鳥噉食，
<lb ed="T" n="0796c08"/>肉盡骨乾，髑髏異處。此是苦不？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0796c0813" rend="inline">答言：「實是大
<lb ed="T" n="0796c09"/>苦。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796c0902">「何謂恩愛別苦？室家內外，兄弟妻子，共
<lb ed="T" n="0796c10"/>相戀慕，一朝破亡，為人抄劫，各自分張，父
<lb n="0796c11" ed="T"/>東子西，母南女北，非唯一處，為人奴婢，各
<lb ed="T" n="0796c12"/>自悲呼，心內斷絕，窈窈冥冥，無有相見之
<lb n="0796c13" ed="T"/>期。此是苦不？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796c1306">答言：「實是大苦。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796c1312">「何謂所求不
<lb ed="T" n="0796c14"/>得苦？家有<note n="0796042" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">財錢散用＝財物散盡【三】，財物散用【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796042">財錢散用【大】，財物散盡【宋】【元】【明】，財物散用【宮】</note><app n="0796042"><lem wit="【大】">財錢，散用</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">財物散盡</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">財物散用</rdg></app>，追求大官，吏民望得
<lb n="0796c15" ed="T"/>富貴，勤苦求之，求之不止，會遇得之，而作
<lb n="0796c16" ed="T"/>邊境令長。未經幾時，貪取民物，為人告言，
<lb n="0796c17" ed="T"/>一朝有事，檻車載去，欲殺之時，憂苦無量，
<lb ed="T" n="0796c18"/>不知死活何日。此是苦不？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0796c1811" rend="inline">答曰：「實是大苦。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796c1817">「何
<lb n="0796c19" ed="T"/>謂怨憎會苦？世人薄俗，共居愛欲之中，<note n="0796043" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">共諍＝爭【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796043" type="mod" resp="CBETA">共諍【大】，爭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796043"><lem wit="【大】">共
<lb n="0796c20" ed="T"/>諍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">爭</rdg></app>不急之事，更相殺害，遂成<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0796044">大怨＝大然【宋】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0796044">大怨【大】，大然【宋】</note><app n="0796044"><lem wit="【大】">大怨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">大然</rdg></app>，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796045">〔各〕－【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796045">各【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0796045"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>自相
<lb n="0796c21" ed="T"/>避，隱藏無<note n="0796046" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">地＝處【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796046">地【大】，處【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796046"><lem wit="【大】">地</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">處</rdg></app>，各磨刀錯箭，挾弓持杖，恐<note n="0796047" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">畏＝忽【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796047">畏【大】，忽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796047"><lem wit="【大】">畏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">忽</rdg></app>
<lb n="0796c22" ed="T"/>相見，會遇<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0796048">迮＝狹【三】【宮】</note><note n="0796048" type="mod" resp="CBETA">迮【大】，狹【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796048"><lem wit="【大】">迮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">狹</rdg></app>道相逢，<note n="0796049" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔各自〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796049">各自【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0796049"><lem wit="【大】">各自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>張弓<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0796050">㴻＝注【三】，註【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0796050">㴻【大】，注【宋】【元】【明】，註【宮】</note><app n="0796050"><lem wit="【大】">㴻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">注</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">註</rdg></app>箭，兩
<lb n="0796c23" ed="T"/>刀相向，不知勝負是誰，當爾之時，怖畏無量。
<lb ed="T" n="0796c24"/>此是苦不？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0796c2405" rend="inline">答曰：「實是大苦。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0796c2411">「何謂憂悲惱苦？人
<pb xml:id="T14.0523.0797a" n="0797a" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0797a01"/>生在世，長命者乃至百歲，短命者胞胎傷墮。
<lb ed="T" n="0797a02"/>長命之者，與<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0797001">其＝斯【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0797001">其【大】，斯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797001"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">斯</rdg></app>百歲，夜消其半，餘有五十
<lb n="0797a03" ed="T"/>年；在醉酒疾病，不知作人，<note n="0797002" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797002" type="mod" resp="CBETA">以【大】，已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797002"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>減五<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0797003">歲＝年【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0797003">歲【大】，年【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797003"><lem wit="【大】">歲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">年</rdg></app>；小
<lb ed="T" n="0797a04"/>時愚癡；<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0797004">十五年＝五十年【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0797004">十五年【大】，五十年【宮】</note><app n="0797004"><lem wit="【大】">十五年</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">五十年</rdg></app><note n="0797005" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">中＝過【三】</note><note n="0797005" type="mod" resp="CBETA">中【大】，過【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0797005"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">過</rdg></app>，未知禮儀；年<note n="0797006" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">過＝中【三】</note><note n="0797006" type="mod" resp="CBETA">過【大】，中【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0797006"><lem wit="【大】">過</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">中</rdg></app><note n="0797007" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">八十＝十五年中七十【宮】</note><note n="0797007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八十【大】，十五年中七十【宮】</note><app n="0797007"><lem wit="【大】">八
<lb n="0797a05" ed="T"/>十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">十五年中七十</rdg></app>，老<note type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0797008">鈍＝耄【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797008" type="mod" resp="CBETA">鈍【大】，耄【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797008"><lem wit="【大】">鈍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">耄</rdg></app>無<note n="0797009" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">智＝知【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0797009">智【大】，知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797009"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg></app>，耳聾目冥，無有法則，復減
<lb ed="T" n="0797a06"/>二十年；已九十年，過餘<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0797010">〔有〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0797010">有【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797010"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>十歲之中，<note n="0797011" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">多諸憂愁＝多有諸愁憂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797011" type="mod" resp="CBETA">多諸憂愁【大】，多有諸愁憂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797011"><lem wit="【大】">多諸
<lb n="0797a07" ed="T"/>憂愁</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">多有諸愁憂</rdg></app>——天下欲亂時亦愁，天下旱時亦愁，天
<lb ed="T" n="0797a08"/>下大水亦愁，天下大霜亦愁，天下<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0797012">不熟＝大熱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797012" type="mod" resp="CBETA">不熟【大】，大熱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797012"><lem wit="【大】">不熟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">大熱</rdg></app>亦
<lb ed="T" n="0797a09"/>愁，室家內外多諸病痛亦愁，持家財物治生
<lb n="0797a10" ed="T"/>恐失亦愁，官家百調未輸亦愁，家人遭縣官
<lb n="0797a11" ed="T"/>事，閉繫<note n="0797013" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">牢獄＝在獄【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0797013">牢獄【大】，在獄【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797013"><lem wit="【大】">牢獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">在獄</rdg></app>未知出期亦愁，兄弟、妻子遠
<lb n="0797a12" ed="T"/>行未歸亦愁，居家窮寒無有衣食亦愁，比
<lb ed="T" n="0797a13"/>舍村落有事亦愁，社<g ref="#CB01142"/>不辦亦愁，室家死亡
<lb n="0797a14" ed="T"/>無有財物、殯葬亦愁，至春時種作無有犁牛
<lb n="0797a15" ed="T"/>亦愁——如是種種憂<note n="0797014" place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig">悲＝愁【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0797014">悲【大】，愁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797014"><lem wit="【大】">悲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">愁</rdg></app>，常無樂時。至其節日
<lb n="0797a16" ed="T"/>共相集聚，應當<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0797015">歡樂＝歡喜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797015" type="mod" resp="CBETA">歡樂【大】，歡喜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797015"><lem wit="【大】">歡樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">歡喜</rdg></app>，方共悲涕相向。此是
<lb ed="T" n="0797a17"/>苦不？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0797a1703">答曰：「實是大苦。」</p>
<lb n="0797a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0797a1801">爾時，五王及諸群臣，會中數千萬人，聞<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0797016">（佛）＋說【三】【宮】</note><note n="0797016" type="mod" resp="CBETA">說【大】，佛說【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797016"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">佛說</rdg></app>
<lb n="0797a19" ed="T"/>諸苦諦，心開意悟，即得須陀洹道，皆大歡
<lb n="0797a20" ed="T"/>喜，作禮而去。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0797a2006" rend="inline">四王俱白普安王言：「大王真
<lb n="0797a21" ed="T"/>是大權菩薩，化噵我等，令得道跡，大王之
<lb ed="T" n="0797a22"/>恩。我本觀諸宮殿，心情愛著，不能遠離，今
<lb n="0797a23" ed="T"/>覩宮殿，如視穢廁，無可<note n="0797017" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">愛＝樂【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0797017">愛【大】，樂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797017"><lem wit="【大】">愛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">樂</rdg></app>者。」即捨王位付
<lb ed="T" n="0797a24"/>弟，出家為道，修諸功德，日日<note n="0797018" place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho">不＝無【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0797018">不【大】，無【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0797018"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>惓。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0797a25" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說五王經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
